       <div class="section-block" id="section-1">
        <div class="page-header">
         <h1>
          Welcome to Occupational Health
         </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
         <p>
          MSU Occupational Health provides medical assessment, monitoring, intervention, and evaluation to MSU employees related to their occupational risks. The office shares responsibility for the health and safety of the MSU community with the
          <a href="http://www.orcbs.msu.edu/">
           Office of Environmental Health and Safety (EHS)
          </a>
          . These services are required by Federal and State laws. If you do not know whether you have occupational health requirements please contact us.
         </p>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="section-block">
        <h2>
         Resources
        </h2>
        <div class="dropdown">
         <button aria-expanded="false" aria-haspopup="true" class="btn btn-primary dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" type="button">
